      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Strip your<strong> mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Tip: Hold the top of the herb sprigs firmly and slide your fingers down their lengths to easily remove the leaves</p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>cannellini</strong> <strong>beans</strong></p>",
