    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once slightly browned, add the <strong>diced onion</strong> and<strong> chopped garlic</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until slightly softened</p><p>Once slightly softened, add the <strong>drained cannellini beans</strong> with your <strong>tomato paste</strong> and 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
