      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[400ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>to the dish with your <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong>,<strong> soy sauce </strong>and<strong> chicken stock mix</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and <strong>salt </strong>and mix it all together – this is your <strong>sausage and bean filling</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
