            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the sausage and bean filling with the <strong>sliced potatoes</strong> and sprinkle over your <strong>dried thyme</strong></p><p>Put the dish in the oven, lid off, for 20-25 min or until the potatoes and sausages are cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>hearty sausage & baked bean hotpot</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Leave out the dried thyme or only use a little!</span></strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
